<li>Localize food purchases to local growers- decreases the  carbon footprint of travel, and supports local economy.</li>
<li>Implement Re-usable containers at The Crossroads to reduce trash, and increase customer value.</li>
<li>Use compost more effectively. University Food Services currently uses a composting machine that reduces water waste in the food, and we are working on partnering with the BYU-Idaho Ag Center to have the compost used.</li>
<li>Increase student awareness and participation in school  recycling system.</li>
</ol>
